        "NSLocationAlwaysAndWhenInUseUsageDescription": "Justice Gavel uses your location in the background to notify you when someone you are monitoring has been arrested in your county.",
        "NSLocationAlwaysUsageDescription": "Background location is used only for the arrest monitor feature when enabled."
